He said threatening things.  He threw a shelf off my wall about 5
feet...showed up as shadows in the hallway...talking at
night....oppressive tight feeling in my chest if he was active...high emf
readings when he was active..








&gt; Carol, I guess my confusion is over how a ritual works to stop an entity
&gt; intent on causing harm.  I&#39;m someone who prays and meditates often, but I
&gt; wonder if bad spirits are capable of disregarding the boundaries we set
&gt; for them.  I do know that when I told my threatening EVPer to go back
&gt; outside it worked; in fact, I haven&#39;t been able to record ANY EVP in my
&gt; house since then.  I&#39;ve never gotten the cursing so many people describe.
